OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWater pours through pub    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fceiling after pipes burst  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A pub faces a huge clean up operation  
OL,6, after pipes burst, with water pouring  
OL,7, from the ceiling and flooding its      
OL,8, dining room.                           
OL,10,FRichard McGill, manager of The George  
OL,11,Fin Mountain Ash, opened up on Saturday 
OL,12,Fmorning to the sound of rushing water. 
OL,14,F"It's a total mess," he said. "My      
OL,15,Fpartner could hear running water and   
OL,16,Fthought it must be the dishwasher or   
OL,17,Fsomething."                            
OL,19,FWelsh Water said there had been a      
OL,20,Fnumber of leaks due a "rapid thaw".    
